<% content_for :title, "Privacy Policy – Kula HR" %>

<div class="bg-white min-h-screen">
  <!-- Nav -->
  <nav class="border-b border-stone-100 px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <%= link_to root_path, class: "text-xl font-bold text-kula-600" do %>
      Kula HR
    <% end %>
    <%= link_to "← Back to Home", root_path, class: "text-sm text-stone-500 hover:text-stone-700" %>
  </nav>

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-stone-500 mb-10">Last updated: January 1, 2026</p>

    <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none space-y-8 text-stone-700 leading-relaxed">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect information you provide directly to us when you register for an account, use our services, or contact us for support. This includes:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Account information (name, email address, company name)</li>
          <li>Employee data entered into the platform (names, compensation details, tax information)</li>
          <li>Usage data and interaction logs for improving service quality</li>
          <li>Billing and payment information processed securely through our payment provider</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Provide, maintain, and improve the Kula HR platform</li>
          <li>Process payroll computations including statutory deductions (PF, ESI, Professional Tax, TDS)</li>
          <li>Send service-related communications such as payslips and approval notifications</li>
          <li>Comply with applicable Indian labour and tax laws</li>
          <li>Respond to your comments, questions, and customer support requests</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">3. Data Isolation &amp; Multi-Tenancy</h2>
        <p>Each organisation's data is strictly isolated. Tenant data is scoped to your subdomain and is never accessible to other organisations on the platform. Our multi-tenant architecture enforces row-level isolation at the database layer.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">4. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share data only:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>With service providers who assist us in operating the platform (hosting, email delivery)</li>
          <li>When required by law or to comply with legal process</li>
          <li>To protect the rights, property, or safety of Kula HR or our users</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">5. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We retain your data for as long as your account is active or as needed to provide services. You may request deletion of your account and associated data by contacting our support team. Statutory payroll records may be retained as required by Indian law.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">6. Security</h2>
        <p>We implement industry-standard security measures including encryption in transit (TLS), encrypted storage for sensitive fields, and role-based access controls. We conduct regular security reviews and promptly address any identified vulnerabilities.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data. HR Admins can manage employee records directly within the platform. For requests that cannot be fulfilled through the platform, contact us at the email below.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">8. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@kula-hr.com" class="text-kula-600 hover:underline">privacy@kula-hr.com</a>.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer class="border-t border-stone-100 py-8 text-center text-sm text-stone-400">
    <p>&copy; 2026 Kula HR. All rights reserved. &nbsp;·&nbsp;
      <%= link_to "Terms of Service", terms_of_service_path, class: "hover:text-stone-600" %>
    </p>
  </footer>
</div>
